aws:SiteData.aws:Description: FlipKey organizes the reputation of vacation rental properties throughout the world. Thousands of websites promote vacation rentals, but most websites promote the properties who have paid them the most money. At FlipKey we believe reputation, trust and feedback from past guests are the best resources to ensure you rent the ideal vacation home and have a fantastic vacation. Ultimately, FlipKey matches trusted guests with trusted vacation homes. ...
